   FROM probability p
   INNER JOIN ps1_ztf pz ON p.oid = pz.oid
   WHERE p.classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'

          pz.szmag1,
          pz.distpsnr1,
          pz.sg_score1

   INNER JOIN ztf_objects zo ON pz.oid = zo.oid
   WHERE pz.sg_score1 > 0.8 )
SELECT *
FROM ztf_objects
WHERE oid IN
    (SELECT oid
     FROM ps1_closest_objects
     LIMIT 100);

WITH min_diff_g_r AS
  (SELECT candid,
          MIN(sigmag1 - srmag1) AS diff_min_g_r
   FROM ps1_ztf
   GROUP BY candid)
SELECT t1.candid AS ztf_identifier,
       COUNT(*) AS num_detections,
       t1.sigmag1 - t1.srmag1 AS diff_min_g_r,
       t2.w1_w2 AS w1_w2,
       v.version AS feature_version
FROM ps1_ztf t1
JOIN min_diff_g_r mdr ON t1.candid = mdr.candid
LEFT JOIN feature_version v ON t1.candid = v.candidate_id
LEFT JOIN
  (SELECT candid,
          SUM(w1_w2) AS w1_w2
   FROM ps1_ztf
   WHERE W1_W2 < 1
   GROUP BY candid) t2 ON t1.candid = t2.candid
WHERE t1.W1_W2 < 1
LIMIT 100;

WITH periodic_objects AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          o.possibility,
          f.value,
          f.name,
          f.fid,
          fv.version
   FROM OBJECT o
   JOIN feature f ON o.oid = f.oid
   JOIN feature_version fv ON f.version = fv.version
   WHERE o.stellar = FALSE
     AND o.ndet > 0
     AND o.corrected = TRUE
     AND f.name IN ('Periodicity',
                    'VariabilityAmplitude')
     AND f.fid BETWEEN 1 AND 3
     AND f.value > 0.7
     AND f.value < 1.5
     AND f.fid IN (1,
                   2,
                   3)
     AND f.version IN ('v1.0',
                       'v1.1') ),
     periodic_and_yso AS
  (SELECT po.oid,
          po.possibility,
          po.value,
          po.name,
          po.fid,
          pv.version
   FROM periodic_objects po
   JOIN feature_version pv ON po.version = pv.version
   WHERE po.name IN ('Periodicity',
                     'VariabilityAmplitude')
     AND po.value >= 0.5
     AND po.fid IN (1,
                    2,
                    3)
     AND po.version IN ('v1.0',
                        'v1.1') )
SELECT DISTINCT oid,
                possibility,
                value,
                name,
                fid,
                VERSION
FROM periodic_and_yso
ORDER BY possibility DESC;
